  ],
  "risk_analysis": [
    "Sustained uncertain macroeconomic environment due to shifting tariffs and fiscal policy changes could impact demand and cost structure.",
    "Increased operating expenses related to R&D investments in AI and robotics may pressure profitability in the short term."
  ],
  "investment_recommendation": "Investors should exercise caution given the declining revenue and profitability trends, while also considering the potential long-term growth from Tesla's innovations in AI and energy sectors. A close watch on market conditions and operational execution is advised."
